@startuml
title Preparation and training flow

actor User
participant "build_pitch_conditioning_variants.py" as Builder
participant "dataprep" as Dataprep
participant "step_2_encodec.py" as Encodec
participant "step_3_sidecars.py" as Sidecars
participant "step_4_HF.py" as HF
participant "training/loop.py" as Train

User -> Builder: create continuous and categorical variants
Builder -> Builder: quantize pitch and rewrite CSV
Builder --> User: raw datasets prepared

User -> Dataprep: normalize dataset
Dataprep --> User: normalized dataset

User -> Encodec: tokenize audio
Encodec --> User: .ecdc files

User -> Sidecars: create cond.npy
Sidecars --> User: sidecars ready

User -> HF: build hf_dataset
HF --> User: dataset ready for training

User -> Train: train model
Train --> User: checkpoints and logs

@enduml
